addr="algm-001D"
title="Descent data of presheaves">descent data</fr:link> of the cover is a bijection. It is a <fr:strong>separated presheaf</fr:strong> if the map is an injection.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter><fr:tree
